data.description: Beautifully updated home in Widefield! Wood floors on upper level, wood laminate throughout the rest of the home, and ceramic tile in bathrooms. The open-concept kitchen boasts lovely white cabinets, a large island with a breakfast bar and stainless-steel appliances. Currently, the home set up includes two primary bedrooms, both with walk-in closets. A barn door slider separates the main and lower levels. Washer and dryer included! Gorgeous full brick wall with wood burning fireplace and mantel! The backyard is completely fenced! This home is a must-see! Come and take a look today!
